{"tid":427114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潮聯小巴司機：早前收到風  警方今日會加強打擊小巴違泊","createTime":"2017-10-07T08:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T11:08:08.000Z","uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0363959ed1fd67eee96bcd76d14c4ecc3092a5f2","tid":427114,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171007/57301858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171007%2F57301858&d=5bhV4rwtJL9YxTDR13siQv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0ba04423\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171007%2F57301858&h=c82d85dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171007/57301858</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171007/large/1507354124_768a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171007%2Flarge%2F1507354124_768a.jpg&h=c9075424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方舉行全港公共服務車輛安全執法行動，今早11時許，交通警到不時被指有嚴重小巴違泊問題的旺角通菜街一帶，作「抄牌」和驅趕。除專營旺角綫的潮聯小巴外，被「抄」的還包括違泊私家車及貨車。就今早現場所見，過往泊滿3條行車線的潮聯小巴，數目明顯減少，僅使用第一條及部分第二條的行車線。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">司機陳先生負責駕駛潮聯的油塘觀塘紅色小巴，他指自己雖然剛剛開工，但因早前已收到消息，警方會於今日加強執法</span>，「呢度好多小巴，泊第二條（行車）線都算違法，有警察嚟咪走，兜個圈先，或者未坐滿都走」。他認為警方不會因為潮聯，而減輕執法力度，又指擔心會被「抄牌」，故今日會特別小心，否則需多開兩至三轉車補貼罰款。<br />\n<br />\n同屬潮聯小巴綫的紅磡土瓜灣紅色小巴，今早則停泊在通菜街的第二條行車線上。同為陳姓的男司機指，不知自己算不算違法。他提到今早已有警員曾警告過他，但因他留在車上故無被「抄牌」，「佢嚟到就話無司機就抄，你搵司機嚟啦」。他說平日若有警車到場，不少小巴司機都會選擇先行開車離開，如被「抄牌」即等於「白做」一日，「搵得幾百蚊，食埋飯就白做，又唔會做得多，一日9至10轉車，仲有車租」。<br />\n<br />\n而選擇將小巴停泊在花園街的Johnny，今未趕及上班，已先遭警員「抄牌」。他說平日會停泊小巴於停車場內，但由於他昨天休假，替更司機便把小巴泊在花園街，「無所謂啦，呢啲係自己嘅錯，呢度成日抄牌」。Johnny指事前未有收到消息，故不知警方今早會執法，認為需至少多開兩轉車方能補貼罰款。<br />\n<br />\n不過，警方執法過後，下午違泊情況故態復萌。通菜街和花園街約2時的紅色小巴數量明顯增多，分別共佔用三條行車線，不時發生人車爭路，其他經過的車輛只能使用一條行車線。但現場未再見到有警員巡邏和執法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以講吓點解潮聯小巴啲司機可以預早收到風嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d96b7c65fd35cd80f539c8dccd7e4f1f5d9d92","tid":427114,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"有天文台 , 無利益搵鬼信"},{"pid":"f82041900f1ae917604eeb7561e145e267442734","tid":427114,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"潮聯小巴係咪有特權？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b91e7a5dbf32f437d1ac5fba019838f1006d393","tid":427114,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"大家都係拜關老二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94965aeff99b30656128496f2e2bc77c763cd7f","tid":427114,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"有內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c1d4e85559c8dc3130ae9acacfa567ada39d0f","tid":427114,"uid":54371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"因為尋日新聞都有講"},{"pid":"ef9502593914601a0cda847cff1dc5e02f0a6e4f","tid":427114,"uid":51904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"因為人地識睇報紙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1031375/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1031375%2F&d=5bhV4rwtJL9YxTDR13siQv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=9c404698\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1031375%2F&h=25ed3ee4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1031375/</a>"},{"pid":"09019b2a4fd1f0bf50d74e46a08af8633a711c5f","tid":427114,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"平時潮聯班友泊晒三條線唔係好串既咩？"},{"pid":"cddca19379dcb20e77aac81bb2f1443263c28925","tid":427114,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有天文台 , 無利益搵鬼信</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n你冇睇過無間道"},{"pid":"66f1d1a0d9284d7ae2d11e907053dc0a7b2c2755","tid":427114,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:53:49.000Z","msg":"警察怕咗潮聯啦，抄兩三張就收手"},{"pid":"c8cea07dd156c079b35112345a888ec4e242771b","tid":427114,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"警黑巴合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}